==> My approach:
--Caculate final balance per account
SELECT account_id
     , SUM(CASE WHEN transaction_type = 'Deposit' THEN amount
                WHEN transaction_type = 'Withdrawal' THEN -amount END) AS final_balance
FROM transactions 
GROUP BY account_id ;
